snippet.title: Amber Heard Counterclaim Opinion Letter // HA! WE AREN'T BOTS // #justiceforjohnny
snippet.description:
Court released an opinion letter on amber heard counterclaim suit today. Now I'm not a lawyer so this is just my opinion on what I read. I'm really looking forward to her receipts for the donations. 
I'm glad to see the courts denied her claims that Johnny was behind the online petitions which you can find links here:
https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2
http://chng.it/5qpcWw7kd7

Also, link the opinion letter. It comes down to the restraining order of may 2016.
https://www.fairfaxcounty.gov/circuit/sites/circuit/files/assets/documents/pdf/opinions/cl-2019-2911-depp-v-heard-01-24-21.pdf
